videos.description: Devontae Shuler goes up top over the zone and finds Bruce Stevens for the big time dunk.
videos.headline: Stevens flushes alley-oop dunk

videos.description: Terrence Davis receives the pass and knocks down the 3-pointer right at the first-half buzzer.
videos.headline: Davis drains 3 right before the halftime buzzer

videos.description: Arkansas' Daniel Gafford finds Gabe Osabuohien on the baseline for a huge two-handed dunk.
videos.headline: Osabuohien throws down the two-handed jam

videos.description: Ole Miss almost turns it over but it ends up with Breein Tyree, who knocks down the 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Crazy play leads to Ole Miss 3
